&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>MacOS QEMU</title><link>https://artyvr.ru/posts/macos_in_qemu/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 18:01:00 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://artyvr.ru/posts/macos_in_qemu/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="macos-qemu">MacOS QEMU&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Клонируем репозиторий:
&lt;a href="https://github.com/kholia/OSX-KVM">OSX-KVM&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git clone https://github.com/kholia/OSX-KVM.git
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Следуем инструкциям из репозитория.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Для проброса usb-устройств в файл &lt;strong>OpenCore-Boot.sh&lt;/strong> добовляем строку:&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>-device usb-host,bus=ehci.0,vendorid=0x05ac,productid=0x12ab,guest-reset=false,id=iphone&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>в моем случае это iphone/ipad&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Простоя конфигурация Cisco</title><link>https://artyvr.ru/posts/cisco_router_main_config/</link><pubDate>Sat, 26 Apr 2025 18:00:00 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://artyvr.ru/posts/cisco_router_main_config/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>enable
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>write erase
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>reload
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
