&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>arp -an
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Конфигурация H3C</title><link>https://artyvr.ru/posts/h3c_switch_main_config/</link><pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 18:10:00 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://artyvr.ru/posts/h3c_switch_main_config/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
